HEADWORD: Arrowworm
<hw>Ar"row*worm`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A peculiar
transparent worm of the genus <gen>Sagitta</gen>, living at the surface
of the sea. See <er>Sagitta</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

